Uses of Class
org.deidentifier.flash.framework.data.GeneralizationHierarchy

Packages that use GeneralizationHierarchy
org.deidentifier.flash.algorithm This package provides algorithms which traverse the generalization lattice. 
org.deidentifier.flash.framework.check This package implements the core functionality of the FLASH framework, i.e., a highly efficient check for k-anonymity 
org.deidentifier.flash.framework.check.transformer This package provides several transformers that efficiently implement the 'projection' optimization. 
org.deidentifier.flash.framework.data This package implements data management, i.e., encoding and representing input data, output data and generalization hierarchies 
org.deidentifier.flash.metric This package implements several metrics for information loss.
